Test::Bitcoin::Daemon
=====================

This module is meant to be used for testing. It will launch an instance of
bitcoind in a temporary directory at a random port, and provide this
information to the caller so tests that require an RPC connection to a running
bitcoind instance can be run.

INSTALLATION
============

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES
============

This module requires bitcoind from bitcoin.org.

